data.title: Taylor Swift Raises the Roof in Poland, Plus Adele, John Legend, Keegan-Michael Key and More
authors: Alexandra Schonfeld, Vic Verbalaitis, Brendan Le, Luke Chinman, Tanisha Bhat
data.meta_description: From Hollywood to New York and everywhere in between, see what your favorite stars are up to
data.text:
From Hollywood to New York and everywhere in between, see what your favorite stars are up to

Stars have been everywhere this week, from Taylor Swift raising the roof in Warsaw to Adele performing in Munich. John Legend looks dapper in London while Keegan-Michael Key picks up the pieces in New York.

Here, are the best photos of celebs out and about this week. Come back tomorrow for more of the latest A-list outings!
